{"tid":1413134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非們，文宣陣地陣絕不可失！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T08:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T11:08:56.000Z","uid":229880,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"98d65c21a60566365362f22dea851566b535ef0d","tid":1413134,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:57:30.000Z","msg":"警賊現以每日記者會醜化激進示威者，用返2014年佔中果招<br />\n<br />\n想用拉一派打一派做法，<br />\n要和理非同所謂激進示威者切割，<br />\n淡化示威者所追求的理想。<br />\n<br />\n當然，連登唔會中計，因為我地資訊又多又快<br />\n但對好多打工仔黎講，就好容易慢慢被模糊，因為堵路只會愈來愈多<br />\n<br />\n因此，我地未必有勇武派企得咁前<br />\n但製圖airdrop守住大家信念咁，將真相同公眾還原基本<br />\n大家點都要守好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上，文宣要攻警隊好多方面都攻到，如<br />\n1警賊濫權濫捕、<br />\n2誤傷平民、<br />\n3對白衫差別待遇、<br />\n4宿舍高空擲物<br />\n等等違法行為<br />\n<br />\n警賊要試圖淡化自己惡行，<br />\n我地一定要每日同佢地煲大佢<br />\n唔好俾佢地混淆視聽！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，想同各位講<br />\n我係和理非，<br />\n但我只想講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">絕不割蓆！！！！<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"88016e7580325ed166a71b18c094597b2b8038e0","tid":1413134,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:57:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c45162bb97f4cf8e9ccc0ab8d40e20276d2a042f","tid":1413134,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fc7059e7b8a31bdd5b5b6f1676de9b8f10dc71","tid":1413134,"uid":229880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T08:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5622568196a1ac7a241bb76ca5fb83dbf49e